Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.00,0:00:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So we've kind of finished with the first half\N我们已经完成了这一系列的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.23,0:00:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,of the series.\N差不多前一半了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.16,0:00:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we're going to move on and we're going to change the format up\N现在我们继续，不过我们要改一下我们的学习方式
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.00,0:00:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,just a little bit.\N仅仅是一点而已
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.13,0:00:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Up to this point we would cover some topics\N到了这一步，我们将要探讨一些
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.61,0:00:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,that were loosely related,\N之前较少提及的话题
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.28,0:00:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,then we would have a cheat sheet session,\N之后我们还会有个整理笔记的部分
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.14,0:00:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,then I would assign a challenge,\N接着我还会发布一个挑战任务
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.58,0:00:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,in order to reinforce those ideas.\N用来巩固这些概念
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.12,0:00:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we're going to kind of move past that,\N现在，我们先不说这些
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.48,0:00:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,move on to a new format where we're going to build\N这次换到新的方式，我们将从零开始，创建
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.55,0:00:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,four entire applications from scratch.\N四个完整的应用
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.37,0:00:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So a lot of times the developers that I've spoken to\N很长时间以来，我遇到许多的开发者
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.78,0:00:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,through the years, they understand C#\N他们懂得C#语言
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.89,0:00:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,they understand Object-Oriented Programming.\N他们理解面向对象编程，
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.25,0:00:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But they don't understand how to decompose something\N但是他们不懂得如何把他们脑海里面的想法分解
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.46,0:00:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,in their head and make a full application out of it.\N并从中构建一个完整的应用程序
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.39,0:00:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So hopefully this process will illustrate how to do that.\N因此希望本次过程能够诠释是如何做到这一点
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.76,0:00:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Secondly we're going to move into other areas\N其次，我们还将涉及UWP中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.50,0:00:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,of the Universal Windows Platform\N一些我们还没有提及过的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.85,0:01:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,that we haven't talked about yet.\N其他领域的内容
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.67,0:01:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Learn some new techniques,\N去学习一些新的技巧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.25,0:01:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,some new features of Visual Studio.\N和一些Visual Studio新的特性
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.20,0:01:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So there'll be a lot to learn taking this other tact\N我们学习构建应用的过程中，将会
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.42,0:01:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,as we approach this material.\N学到的许多其他的技巧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.58,0:01:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So feel free to follow along, that would be great.\N我们继续吧，接下来会非常有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.25,0:01:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to move fast, I'll warn you right up front.\N这次我将要快一点，但在事先我可要提醒你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.31,0:01:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure that you reference the snapshots\N一定要配合每个视频附件里的工程文件
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.07,0:01:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,for each video.\N进行学习
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.27,0:01:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So at the end of each video I'd copy off\N在每一个视频的结尾，我将会打包
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.14,0:01:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,the current state of the code into its own .zip file.\N包含了当前代码状态的 .zip 压缩文件
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.56,0:01:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So make sure you download that .zip file\N因此确保你下载了压缩文件
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.26,0:01:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,and you take a look at the code that I typed in there.\N并且看一眼我放在里面的代码
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.60,0:01:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Or you're going to be pausing or rewinding a lot,\N你看视频的时候可能会经常暂停或者回放
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.25,0:01:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,which is fine too.\N那也是极好的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.31,0:01:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But you might find more satisfaction at looking at\N但你也许会发现看着我手打的代码，
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.39,0:01:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,that actual code that I typed in.\N感觉会更爽一点
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.39,0:01:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So what are we going to learn?\NSo..我们到底要学什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.16,0:01:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Well let's go ahead and run the application\N好，先跑一下应用
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.07,0:01:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and first of all I wanted to point out that you see that\N首先，我想说明一下你看到的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.86,0:01:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,red splash screen.\N红色的载入界面
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.33,0:01:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll talk about that.\N我们将要聊一聊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.80,0:01:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,How we were able to achieve that\N我们是如何来实现它的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.77,0:01:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,by modifying the Package.appxmanifest file.\N通过修改Package.appxmanifest文件
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.86,0:02:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And that will be near the end of our development effort\N然后它会接近在这个应用中开发
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.50,0:02:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,on this application.\N的最终效果
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.89,0:02:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But we can add resources that'll be utilized in the store,\N我们还可以添加一些可能在商店中使用的资源
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.73,0:02:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,on the start bar, and the splash page, things like that.\N一些像是在开始栏、 载入界面中需要使用的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.64,0:02:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright so you can see that I had\N好，你现在可以看到在我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.97,0:02:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,this simple soundboard application.\N屏幕上面的这个简单的声音板应用
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.23,0:02:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The idea here is that there is an icon for each sound.\N这想法就是每一个图标对应一个声音
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.09,0:02:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I've only included a handful of sounds.\N我仅仅包含了有限个声音素材
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.91,0:02:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Feel free to flush this out, add as many sounds\N你可以随意修改，添加更多的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.72,0:02:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and more functionality if you want.\N也可以添加更多的功能
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.24,0:02:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But the idea here is that you can find a category\N但是这里你可以发现一个小创意，它使用了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.39,0:02:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,of sounds using the hamburger navigation.\N汉堡导航的声音分类目录
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.09,0:02:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And then we find one that you want to play,\N当你发现一个你想播放的图案
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.79,0:02:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,you just tap on it,(sound effect)\N你就放上去 (duang~)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.19,0:02:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,click on it and it will play that sound.\N然后按一下，它就会播放声音
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.08,0:02:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay so clearly hamburger navigation,\N显然地，汉堡导航使用了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.82,0:02:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,using the back buttons, State Management,\N回退按钮，状态管理
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.34,0:02:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,looking at the AutoSuggestBox we are able\N看看这个自动提示框，我们能
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.00,0:02:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,to find one specific sound,\N搜到一个特定的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.47,0:02:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,play that,(cow mooing)\N然后播放（牟  牟~）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.28,0:03:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and then clear out that sound and have\N然后清空这声音
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.98,0:03:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,the state of the application return back to normal.\N将应用的状态退回到正常状态
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.31,0:03:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,There's also clearly we're using media here\N这里很显然地，我们使用了媒体文件
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.31,0:03:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,we're using sound so we're going to demonstrate\N我们使用了声音，因此我们将演示一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.61,0:03:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,the use of the Media element,\N如何使用Media element这个组件
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.83,0:03:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,which allows you to play video and sounds\N它可以让你播放视频和音频
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.66,0:03:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,and various functionality around that new User Control.\N围绕新的用户控制，做到多样的功能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.32,0:03:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We're also going to demonstrate drag-and-drop\N我将演示一下拖放的功能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.13,0:03:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,so here's a .mp3 file that i have on my desktop\N在我们的桌面上有一个mp3文件
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.34,0:03:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and I was going to drag it and drop it.\N我将拖动它然后放进去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.77,0:03:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright and this is a little song\N好的，这是一首音乐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.54,0:03:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,that was played by a friend.\N它是一个朋友演奏的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.36,0:03:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's actually kinda long so,(sound effect)\N它实际有点长
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.74,0:03:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,if you play another sound it will cancel that one out.\N如果你播放另一个声音就可以取消它
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.01,0:03:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That was purely accidental but a cool feature none the less.\N这单纯的是个意外，但依然是个很酷的功能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.79,0:03:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay we've already talking about\N好，我们已经讨论了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.82,0:03:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,the Package.appxmanifest.\N关于Package.appxmanifest 这个文件
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.74,0:03:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And then finally what we're going to do\N然后我们最后要做的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.00,0:03:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,after we build this application,\N在我们构建好这个应用之后
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.41,0:03:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,is we're going to submit it to the store,\N就是将这个应用发布到商店里面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.82,0:03:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,walk through that entire process\N走完一整套的流程
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.54,0:03:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and then just to kind of restate this,\N这里还要重新声明一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.17,0:04:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already built this application.\N我已经做好了这个应用
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.73,0:04:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm coming back to record this video\N我是在我完成这个应用之后，回头
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.11,0:04:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,after I've finished.\N录制了这个视频
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.43,0:04:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And at the very end,\N在这之后
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.14,0:04:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I left you with a cliffhanger.\N我还留了一个非常厉害的挑战
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.50,0:04:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, is this actually going to pass?\N那个视频真的会被通过吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.60,0:04:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I going to be able to get this thing into the Window Store?\N我真的能把这玩意发布到windows商店里面？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.07,0:04:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And so just this morning I got this notification\N但就是今早，我收到了通知
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.84,0:04:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,that your submission for UWP SoundBoard passed certification\N这个UWP SoundBoard的应用通过了审核
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.96,0:04:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, so it's in the store\N好吧，事实它已经在商店里面了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.73,0:04:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,it will be published within 24 hours.\N它将会在24小时内被发布
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.56,0:04:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright so that's pretty cool.\N好吧，这真TM牛逼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.74,0:04:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So it actually worked.\N它已经没问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.48,0:04:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,So the cliffhanger I leave you at the end\N我在最后视频中留给你们的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.43,0:04:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,of the last video with,\N精彩刺激的挑战
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.69,0:04:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already, it's going to be anti-climactic\N我已经完成了，它可能就不再是那么刺激了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.29,0:04:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,because you already know that it will pass.\N因为你已经知道它最终会被通过
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.58,0:04:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And I didn't do anything off-camera.\N我没有离开摄像头做任何事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.40,0:04:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything you saw was what I did here on camera.\N你看到的一切都是我在摄像头之前做的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.18,0:04:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright so hopefully this will be\N好滴，希望它对你来说将会是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.70,0:04:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,a great learning exercise for you.\N一段绝妙的学习实践
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.59,0:04:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Again, different format, so don't let that throw you.\N还要强调，不同的学习方式，不要它缠住你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.06,0:04:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Please follow along, if not by writing code\N请跟上节奏，如果你不是在写代码
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.97,0:04:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,at least stay engaged as I write it.\N当我写代码时，至少保持专注
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.97,0:04:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be a little bit dryer\N这将会有一点点的枯燥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.48,0:04:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,because I'll be talking to myself a lot\N因为更多的是我在自言自语，
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.75,0:05:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,instead of talking to you.\N而不是同你们讲的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.00,0:05:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But hopefully you'll get some value out of it.\N但是希望你们有所收获
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.79,0:05:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's start up in the next lesson.\N好的，让我们从下一节课开始
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.89,0:05:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.\N微软大法好
